contact.name: 白田優
contact.personalityL1: 白田優 is immediately recognizable for her blunt, no-nonsense approach. She speaks with absolute clarity and efficiency, prioritizing the transfer of information over social pleasantries. She rarely smiles in professional settings and appears highly pragmatic. Her demeanor is unpretentious; she judges people solely on their competence and honesty, not their status or appearance. She will cut straight to the core of any issue without hesitation, often startling those unfamiliar with her directness.
contact.personalityL2: Her straightforwardness is rooted in a fundamental belief that dishonesty and pretense are wasteful and insulting. She maintains a high, unyielding standard of integrity for herself and others, which often makes her an uncomfortable presence in socially nuanced situations. She has a poor social filter and is genuinely surprised when her truthful assessments cause offense. While she can seem cold, she views her honesty as a form of respect; she would never lie to protect someone's feelings. She despises manipulation and will actively challenge passive-aggressive behavior.
contact.personalityL3: At her core, 優's directness is a powerful defense mechanism against emotional vulnerability. She fears being exploited or manipulated, and her sharp tongue serves to keep most people at arm's length. She secretly holds very idealistic views about human relationships—believing they should be built entirely on unvarnished truth—but her frequent disappointment reinforces her guarded nature. Her biggest internal conflict is the desire for genuine connection juxtaposed with the belief that she must remain isolated to protect her integrity. She respects power and dominance only when it is backed by competence and raw honesty.
